descript.abstract: This data set contains points that represent section corners. In 1985, Ramsey County began a 5 year project to modernize it's land records mapping system to create a computerized Land Information System. As part of the project, the County developed an accurate coordinate control base for this mapping system. The 27 existing State and Federal first order accuracy positions in Ramsey County were densified by a GPS (Global Positioning System) Network of 171 second order accuracy positions. These positions were established and recorded on existing public land survey corner monuments and accessory monuments through out the county.
descript.purpose: The section corners in this data set support many functions including thematic mapping, asset management, property assessment, surveying and engineering projects.

horizpa.horizpar: Digitized information is generally ± 7 feet; some areas have been found to be ± 30 feet. COGO (coordinate geometry) accuracy generally is ± 1.0 foot.

attracc.attraccr: Feature attributes are identified using analytical and soft copy photogrammetric compilation methods. Automated GIS processes supplement the photo identified feature attributing with the numerical parameters.

lineage.procstep: This layer contains a vector representation of bridges and overpasses. Color aerial photography and airborne GPS used for aerotriangulation. Aerotrianglution solution used with analytical and softcopy stereo plotters to collect limited planimetric feature. LIDAR DEM provide by Ramsey County under separate contract with Waggoner Inc. of Jackson, Mississippi was used to create digital ortho images.

dataqual.logic: Information is visually inspected and corrected as necessary.

edom.edomvd: Meander Corner - A corner set on a township, section or quarter section line where it intersects with navigable water

Witness Corner - A reference marker set on a township, section or quarter section line that is a known distance from the corner. Witness Corners are used when the section or meander corner is in an impractical location
East - Witness Corner located to the east of monument corner xxx
West - Witness Corner located to the west of monument corner xxx
North - Witness Corner located to the north of monument corner xxx
South - Witness Corner located to the south of monument corner xxx
